title: Raxco PerfectDisk Server v14.0 Build 890
description:
Raxco PerfectDisk Server v14.0 Build 890

PerfectDisk® 14 Server speeds up server processing times and dramatically reduces backup times. New Features include Windows Event Log Integration and Thin-Provisioned Drive Auto-Detection. 

    NEW! Windows Event Log Integration
    NEW! Thin Provisioned Drive Auto-Detection
    Increased flexibility in customizable scheduling
    Enhanced SSD reporting and recommendations
    Optimize server performance & reduce backup times

    Extend system life and reduce hardware costs
    ReFS & Cluster Shared Volumes (CSVFS) Support
    OptiWrite™ for fragmentation prevention
    Includes PerfectDisk Enterprise Console
    Smart Bundle Includes 1 Server License and 5 Professional Licenses

Full feature list: http://www.raxco.com/business/products/perfectdisk-server#details
